cdata.name: KuBitX
cdata.desc:
KuBitXis a multi cryptocurrency exchange platform. It provides the users with the tools to trade (buy/sell) cryptocurrencies between them as well as to store, monitor and manage their digital assets using theKuBitX wallets, which is available on Kubitx.

The KBX token is an Ehereum-based (ERC-20) cryptocurrency. It is a utility token that can serve the users as a mean to pay for transactions fees with up to 25% discount when using KuBitX.
